<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!--
    ### Quick documentation ###

    # General stuff

    Background: the image that will be used for the background
    Fonts: list of fonts to use (the "Name" part is simply the name that displays at the top when you preview the font)
    Colors: the color settings (do not change the value of "Key")
    Inventory: Defines the inventory items/equipment/other

    # Inventory
    Font: the font index to use when drawing text
    Tiers: the different tier of the current item (example for OoT's bow: "30;40;50")
    Pos: the position of the current item, in the format "Pos X;Pos Y" (example: 0;0 for top-left corner)
    -> if "Sources" contains only one item the first one will be used by default
    -> use ``;`` to separate the filenames/tiers values
-->
